26:57.867 --> 26:59.285
Betty Cragdale.

26:59.327 --> 27:00.745
So I get to hear you play.

27:00.786 --> 27:02.455
Does your girlfriend
know about this?

27:02.496 --> 27:03.664
THOMAS:
Don't ask, don't tell.

27:03.706 --> 27:05.374
DAISUKE:
Hailey.

27:05.416 --> 27:06.834
-Hey.
-Hi.

27:06.876 --> 27:08.377
Daisuke, congratulations.

27:08.419 --> 27:09.670
You really deserved it.

27:09.712 --> 27:11.547
Thanks.

27:11.589 --> 27:13.090
What happened out there?

27:13.132 --> 27:15.217
You were a different conductor.

27:15.259 --> 27:16.594
Yeah.

27:16.635 --> 27:18.346
I choked.

27:18.387 --> 27:20.056
Sure.

27:20.097 --> 27:21.557
We are not robots.

27:21.599 --> 27:23.768
-Yeah.
